CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 10, 1965, pg. 19 reads: "Labor, Management Team Up - Operator W. E. Broadus takes time out while labor management representatives Frank W. O'Brien, president of Local 1943, USW; James Huntermark, president of Local 1272, USW, and C. Donald Engel and H.P. Saxer, representing J&L management, discuss plans for the huge Health-O-Rama parking lot which will accommodate hundreds of visitors for the forthcoming program scheduled to be held at South Side Recreating Center. April 8-11 - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: W. E. Broadus, seated in construction vehicle, Frank W. O'Brien, James Huntermark, C. Donald Engel, and H.P. Saxer, posed in empty lot to be used for Health-O-Rama parking lot, South Side
